BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun quintile Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Aries 12°26’) - quintile - Natal Mars \n \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 7th house: \nDuring this transit, attention will shift from you to relationships with other people.  \nThere may be a positive shift in romantic relationships. You will communicate better with your partner, enjoy time together and make yourselves happy. If you are experiencing a crisis in your romantic relationship, you may decide to go through counselling, or you may be able to solve the problem by yourselves. If you are single, it is the perfect time to start dating! You will be very popular among friends and you will cooperate with others more effectively. You won’t want to spend too much time alone, because interpersonal relationships will bring you joy.  \nIf you are dealing with legal matters, it is very important to resolve them and reach a successful conclusion, or at least try to do so.  \nYou might also often contemplate bringing more harmony into your life. So, if you have spent a lot of time at work so far, you will try to bring more fun and joy to your personal life, or you will focus more on your partner and friends.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260402T041300Z
DTEND:20260402T041300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:1_tr_su_qu_ma
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars square Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Pisces 24°26’) - square - Natal Mars \nAn unexpected competition may arise with which you will not have the strength and desire to fight. This will give you feelings of frustration and fatigue. Burnout, headaches and stress are possible. If your anger is suppressed, it is possible that it will now come to the surface.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 6th house: \nYou will have an unusually high amount of energy  which you can use at work. The amount of work you can do now is impressive. You will work well especially if you feel that you can identify with goals and values of the project. You may also start thinking about starting your own business. Take care of yourself and watch out for injuries, fever and emotional strain. Try to think more about what you eat; healthy diet will improve your digestion and overall health.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260402T162700Z
DTEND:20260402T162700Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:2_tr_ma_sq_ma
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 4°24’) - sextile - Natal Venus \nYou will spend time in a pleasant company of other people, and it is highly unlikely that you will be involved in any misunderstandings and quarrels. You will be in a great mood, which will increase your popularity. You may gain large sums of money from your investments.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 7th house: \nYou and your partner will be very much in love. You will prefer to spend time only the two of you rather than go out with friends. If you are single, you will be keen to start a new, functioning relationship and find a new partner. In relationships with other people you will use flattery to get what you want. However, be honest! If you are fighting with your partner or a close friend, you will probably reconcile your problems and make up. It is an ideal time for marriage and business partnerships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260403T060300Z
DTEND:20260403T060300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:3_tr_ve_se_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus quincunx Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 5°03’) - quincunx - Natal Pluto \n \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 7th house: \nYou and your partner will be very much in love. You will prefer to spend time only the two of you rather than go out with friends. If you are single, you will be keen to start a new, functioning relationship and find a new partner. In relationships with other people you will use flattery to get what you want. However, be honest! If you are fighting with your partner or a close friend, you will probably reconcile your problems and make up. It is an ideal time for marriage and business partnerships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260403T183200Z
DTEND:20260403T183200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:4_tr_ve_qu_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus sextile Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Taurus 28°55’) - sextile - Natal Mercury \nThis transit will give you a new perspective on old issues and problems. If you have been struggling to solve a difficult problem for a long time, a breakthrough may now occur. It is a good time for traveling because it will bring you exciting experiences.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit Uranus brings unexpected developments in the area of finance. However, this does not involve the money you earn; it involves money you share with your partner (romantic or business), loans, alimony, taxes etc. People with whom you have a close relationship and whom you depend on financially may experience a period of financial instability. You may also start experimenting with your sexuality and change your opinion about intimate relationships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260404T135600Z
DTEND:20260404T135600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:5_tr_ur_se_me
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars quincunx Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Pisces 25°58’) - quincunx - Natal Uranus \n \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 6th house: \nYou will have an unusually high amount of energy  which you can use at work. The amount of work you can do now is impressive. You will work well especially if you feel that you can identify with goals and values of the project. You may also start thinking about starting your own business. Take care of yourself and watch out for injuries, fever and emotional strain. Try to think more about what you eat; healthy diet will improve your digestion and overall health.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260404T154200Z
DTEND:20260404T154200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:6_tr_ma_qu_ur
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 7°26’) - sextile - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit will make you feel happy and satisfied. You will enjoy even the slightest pleasure and pass this feeling on to others. Nothing will upset you. You may also feel a bit lazy and seek pleasure. Your relationships will flourish. In the area of finance, you may make a good investment, or you may get a great opportunity to acquire finances. If you are dealing with legal issues, this transit will contribute to a satisfactory outcome. It is a great time for social events, excursions or a vacation.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 7th house: \nYou and your partner will be very much in love. You will prefer to spend time only the two of you rather than go out with friends. If you are single, you will be keen to start a new, functioning relationship and find a new partner. In relationships with other people you will use flattery to get what you want. However, be honest! If you are fighting with your partner or a close friend, you will probably reconcile your problems and make up. It is an ideal time for marriage and business partnerships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260405T171600Z
DTEND:20260405T171600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:7_tr_ve_se_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun quintile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Aries 17°22’) - quintile - Natal Saturn \n \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 7th house: \nDuring this transit, attention will shift from you to relationships with other people.  \nThere may be a positive shift in romantic relationships. You will communicate better with your partner, enjoy time together and make yourselves happy. If you are experiencing a crisis in your romantic relationship, you may decide to go through counselling, or you may be able to solve the problem by yourselves. If you are single, it is the perfect time to start dating! You will be very popular among friends and you will cooperate with others more effectively. You won’t want to spend too much time alone, because interpersonal relationships will bring you joy.  \nIf you are dealing with legal matters, it is very important to resolve them and reach a successful conclusion, or at least try to do so.  \nYou might also often contemplate bringing more harmony into your life. So, if you have spent a lot of time at work so far, you will try to bring more fun and joy to your personal life, or you will focus more on your partner and friends.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260407T043800Z
DTEND:20260407T043800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:8_tr_su_qu_sa
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus quincunx Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 9°22’) - quincunx - Natal Neptune \n \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit you will feel the desire for a deep intimate bond with your loved ones. You will be attracted to the people with something mysterious about them; perhaps you will feel a bit stirred by them. Shallow people will not deserve your attention now. Sexual relationships will deepen and make you feel much younger and full of energy. You may feel an increase in sexual energy. You may also see a psychologist or meet someone who is one during this transit. \nIn your romantic relationship you will deal with various issues, including intimacy, finance, and power distribution. It is possible that either you or your partner will want to move your commitment to the next level.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260407T070500Z
DTEND:20260407T070500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:9_tr_ve_qu_ne
END:VEVENT
