DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 9°26’) - octile - Natal Mars \n \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit you will feel the desire for a deep intimate bond with your loved ones. You will be attracted to the people with something mysterious about them; perhaps you will feel a bit stirred by them. Shallow people will not deserve your attention now. Sexual relationships will deepen and make you feel much younger and full of energy. You may feel an increase in sexual energy. You may also see a psychologist or meet someone who is one during this transit. \nIn your romantic relationship you will deal with various issues, including intimacy, finance, and power distribution. It is possible that either you or your partner will want to move your commitment to the next level.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
