SUMMARY:Tr. Mars conjunction Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Pisces 28°55’) - conjunction - Natal Mercury \nYou may meet a lot of irritated people, especially if you work with them. Or it may be you who will be irritable and impulsive. Be particularly careful when driving because you are prone to unpredictable responses and you could be fined (e.g. for fast driving). Be careful when handling sharp objects.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 6th house: \nYou will have an unusually high amount of energy  which you can use at work. The amount of work you can do now is impressive. You will work well especially if you feel that you can identify with goals and values of the project. You may also start thinking about starting your own business. Take care of yourself and watch out for injuries, fever and emotional strain. Try to think more about what you eat; healthy diet will improve your digestion and overall health.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
