BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun conjunction Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Aries 20°41’) - conjunction - Natal Sun \nToday you will be more reflective and feel the desire to set long-term goals and resolutions - for example start exercising. You will have more energy and determination than ever. You will also want to be the centre of attention. \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 7th house: \nDuring this transit, attention will shift from you to relationships with other people.  \nThere may be a positive shift in romantic relationships. You will communicate better with your partner, enjoy time together and make yourselves happy. If you are experiencing a crisis in your romantic relationship, you may decide to go through counselling, or you may be able to solve the problem by yourselves. If you are single, it is the perfect time to start dating! You will be very popular among friends and you will cooperate with others more effectively. You won’t want to spend too much time alone, because interpersonal relationships will bring you joy.  \nIf you are dealing with legal matters, it is very important to resolve them and reach a successful conclusion, or at least try to do so.  \nYou might also often contemplate bringing more harmony into your life. So, if you have spent a lot of time at work so far, you will try to bring more fun and joy to your personal life, or you will focus more on your partner and friends.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260410T133200Z
DTEND:20260410T133200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:16_tr_su_co_su
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Pisces 24°26’) - square - Natal Mars \nBeware of distraction, irritability and acting impulsively. You can easily get into conflict, or you can meet critical and aggressive people. Therefore, it is better to avoid negotiating and compromising. You will do well in debates, but you will not be too diplomatic, and you may say something inappropriate. Your ability to listen will be suppressed, and you may often forget to wait for your turn while talking or react irritably to arguments of other people. In short, you will want to have everything done right away and not to slow things down by too much talking. Therefore, it is not a good time for any business meetings or the start of a new project. Beware of sharp objects and complications when travelling by car.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 6th house: \nThis transit is good for organising your work activities and duties. You will approach them practically, attentively and with a sense for detail. You will enjoy your work more than usual and it will also give you more satisfaction. Communication with colleagues and clients will become easier. However, beware of unimportant conversations that undermine work ethic and efficiency. You may also encounter technical issues and shipment delays.  \nYou will pay more attention to your health. It is an ideal time to plan medical examinations. Nervousness and fear may cause physical tension. However, these health problems are usually not real, they are likely only in your head. Being aware of the cause of your nervousness will easily help you overcome it. You may also visit a hospital, psychiatric institution or prison during this transit. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260410T234500Z
DTEND:20260410T234500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:17_tr_me_sq_ma
END:VEVENT
