DTEND:20260423T064500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:48_tr_ve_se_me
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury quintile Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Aries 12°26’) - quintile - Natal Mars \n \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
