BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus semisextile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Taurus 29°22’) - semisextile - Natal Saturn \n \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit you will feel the desire for a deep intimate bond with your loved ones. You will be attracted to the people with something mysterious about them; perhaps you will feel a bit stirred by them. Shallow people will not deserve your attention now. Sexual relationships will deepen and make you feel much younger and full of energy. You may feel an increase in sexual energy. You may also see a psychologist or meet someone who is one during this transit. \nIn your romantic relationship you will deal with various issues, including intimacy, finance, and power distribution. It is possible that either you or your partner will want to move your commitment to the next level.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260423T154600Z
DTEND:20260423T154600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:50_tr_ve_se_sa
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun sextile Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Taurus 4°24’) - sextile - Natal Venus \nDuring this time, you are more charming and attractive than usual. You are enjoying the attention of others. You are also being very generous. You are dealing with financial matters effectively and thriving in your love life. You can expect an invitation to a party or other social event.  \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 7th house: \nDuring this transit, attention will shift from you to relationships with other people.  \nThere may be a positive shift in romantic relationships. You will communicate better with your partner, enjoy time together and make yourselves happy. If you are experiencing a crisis in your romantic relationship, you may decide to go through counselling, or you may be able to solve the problem by yourselves. If you are single, it is the perfect time to start dating! You will be very popular among friends and you will cooperate with others more effectively. You won’t want to spend too much time alone, because interpersonal relationships will bring you joy.  \nIf you are dealing with legal matters, it is very important to resolve them and reach a successful conclusion, or at least try to do so.  \nYou might also often contemplate bringing more harmony into your life. So, if you have spent a lot of time at work so far, you will try to bring more fun and joy to your personal life, or you will focus more on your partner and friends.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260424T141200Z
DTEND:20260424T141200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:51_tr_su_se_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun quincunx Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Taurus 5°03’) - quincunx - Natal Pluto \n \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 7th house: \nDuring this transit, attention will shift from you to relationships with other people.  \nThere may be a positive shift in romantic relationships. You will communicate better with your partner, enjoy time together and make yourselves happy. If you are experiencing a crisis in your romantic relationship, you may decide to go through counselling, or you may be able to solve the problem by yourselves. If you are single, it is the perfect time to start dating! You will be very popular among friends and you will cooperate with others more effectively. You won’t want to spend too much time alone, because interpersonal relationships will bring you joy.  \nIf you are dealing with legal matters, it is very important to resolve them and reach a successful conclusion, or at least try to do so.  \nYou might also often contemplate bringing more harmony into your life. So, if you have spent a lot of time at work so far, you will try to bring more fun and joy to your personal life, or you will focus more on your partner and friends.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260425T055700Z
DTEND:20260425T055700Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:52_tr_su_qu_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars quintile Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Aries 12°26’) - quintile - Natal Mars \n \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit will try to teach you the importance of compromise. Try to avoid unnecessary conflicts with your partner and realize that two people are better off when they work together. Your partner, friend or business partner will now require more attention than usual. This can lead to feelings of frustration stemming from losing free time. However, you will still be happy about your relationship and think about whether it is time to move your relationship to the next level. If you have feared the commitment, you will be more optimistic about it now. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260425T205600Z
DTEND:20260425T205600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:53_tr_ma_qu_ma
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury quintile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Aries 17°22’) - quintile - Natal Saturn \n \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260426T051100Z
DTEND:20260426T051100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165124Z
UID:54_tr_me_qu_sa
END:VEVENT
