BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury sextile Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Aries 24°26’) - sextile - Natal Mars \nThis transit will make you unbeatable at work. You will work with a lot of enthusiasm and so much energy that you will not mind staying overtime to complete what is needed. You will look at things with a clear mind and you will not miss any detail. This enthusiasm and energy will also manifest itself in communicating with people around you. You will be spontaneous and pleasant. If you need to get someone on your side or persuade somebody about something, it’s a good time. Your arguments will be totally bulletproof. \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
